node.text: We’ve heard it all before, practice makes perfect. I am mature enough to look at that practice and tear it apart. Join me in my favorite game of ‘Remember Her’ taking a look back at the mugs that have helped my evolution.

node.text: We’re taking a trip down memory lane. It’s not always glam, but we have to respect the growth. From harsh colors and beady eyes to too much lip gloss and blue contacts; the Naomi face has been all over the place.
